{"tid":726181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大隻多肌肉就等於好打呢個concept錯撚哂","createTime":"2018-07-02T07:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T07:49:35.000Z","uid":94923,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5286fd582629cf28bb4f5f8769bd29954d0c62d1","tid":726181,"uid":94923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"1feb6b6c344a84584acd9608233ecce120aa7c6d","tid":726181,"uid":61443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"有冇10年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5827f36479371c80f218339d2377771b257c1fd8","tid":726181,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">OLD</span></span>"},{"pid":"bff48886cefb95ebc1f7f466f81ef0316238d209","tid":726181,"uid":94923,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"真人真事"}]}